<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">About</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-8 sm:gap-10 lg:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-base text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 sm:text-lg">
          MitchCo Construction, Inc. was started by Mitch Joa in 1989. We have been successfully
          meeting the needs of commercial property owners alike for over 30 years for one simple
          reason: we understand the demands of this industry. After decades of experience providing
          our customers quality snow removal services, we know how and when to clear and de-ice your
          lot to keep your business open and your customers safe.
